          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "During their careers, Shirkey and Chatfield have received nearly $140,000 from the DeVos family. Those donations represent only a fraction of the money the DeVos family has delivered to Michigan Republican legislators who could decide the fate of the state’s elector slate.",
